// ⟦axhrv_variable⟧
{burd_tools_dir}

Path to the project tools root directory, derived from BURC_TOOLS_DIR during dispatch setup.
Exported by bud_dispatch.sh and survives the exec boundary into CLI processes.
CLIs use this to locate utilities without re-sourcing BURC.

// ⟦axhrv_variable⟧
{burd_buk_dir}

Path to the BUK subdirectory, derived as BURC_TOOLS_DIR/buk during dispatch setup.
Exported by bud_dispatch.sh and survives the exec boundary into CLI processes.

// ⟦axhrv_variable⟧
{burd_tabtarget_dir}

Path to the tabtarget directory, derived from BURC_TABTARGET_DIR during dispatch setup.
Exported by bud_dispatch.sh and survives the exec boundary into CLI processes.

